In a Dutch oven over medium heat, cook bacon until browned, 10 minutes. Add onion; cook until soft, 5 minutes. Add cabbage, apple, vinegar, and 1/4 cup water. Cook, stirring, until cabbage wilts, 5 minutes. Season with salt and pepper. Cover; cook, stirring occasionally, over medium-low heat to desired softness (if sticking, add water), 45 minutes to 1 hour.